'''''Potomanto''''' (yakomotse ku ijambo ry'igifaransa ''portmanteau'' ) ni filime yo muri [[Gana|Gana ya]] 2013 - [[Nijeriya]] yerekana ibikorwa bya Shirley Frimpong Manso<ref>Potomanto (2013) | MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › potomanto</ref> . Irimo Olu Jacobs, Yvonne Okoro na Adjetey Anang <ref>potomanto - Ghana Film Industry <nowiki>https://www.ghanafilmindustry.com</nowiki> › tag › potomanto</ref>.  Yerekanwe bwa mbere muri Sinema ya Silverbird, [[Accra]], muri [[Gana]], ku ya 20 Ukuboza 2013.<ref>Watch Shirley Frimpong Manso's POTOMANTO In FULL HD ... <nowiki>https://www.ghanacelebrities.com</nowiki> › 2013/12/25 › perfe...</ref>  

== Umugambi ==
Uwahoze ari umupolisi urakaye, Andane, akazi ke ni ugukora iperereza no gufata abafatanyabikorwa bahemutse afata indi sura iyo yahawe akazi ko gukora iperereza ku mugore w’umucuruzi ukize<ref>My Thoughts On Shirley Frimpong Manso's New Movie ... (ghanacelebrities.com)</ref>. Yatsitaye ku mpeta y'abasaruzi b'ingingo n'abacuruzi bashuka abasore babasezeranya kubajyana mu mahanga<ref>World Cinema Amsterdam <nowiki>https://worldcinemaamsterdam.nl</nowiki> › Films › us-in-between</ref>. Umukwe wumukire numukozi wihishe nawe ukora iperereza kugirango afate abacuruza urugingo<ref>What You Need To Know About The Film Industry In Ghana <nowiki>https://www.demandafrica.com</nowiki> › entertainment › gholl...</ref>. Bishyize hamwe bagerageza guhagarika kanseri yatwaye ubuzima bwa benshi mu rubyiruko mu baturage<ref>Shirley Frimpong-Manso - Wikipedia <nowiki>http://yamm.finance</nowiki> › wiki › Shirley_Frimpong-Manso</ref>. 

